firefly
------------------------------------------
Standalone C++ Library for vectors calculations

Runtime requirements:

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libgtest-devel-1.17.0-1bl1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/tbhaxor/firefly

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/tbhaxor/firefly/archive/refs/tags/v3.1.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack firefly-3.1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./firefly-3.1.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/firefly-3.1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/firefly-3.1.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(firefly)
  /usr/include/firefly/utilities.hpp
  /usr/include/firefly/vector.hpp
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/firefly.README
  /usr/share/doc/firefly/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/firefly/README.md

------------------

